<section type="preface">
HEc est Regula gen<expan type="">er</expan>alis
p<expan type="">ro</expan> toto libro om<expan type="">n</expan>ia no<expan type="">m</expan>i<expan type="">n</expan>a
verbalia et participia
h<expan type="">ab</expan>ent significac<expan type="">i</expan>o<expan type="">n</expan>em v<expan type="">er</expan>bor<expan type="">um</expan> a quibus
discendu<expan type="">n</expan>t secu<expan type="">n</expan>dum eor<expan type="">um</expan> forma<expan type="">m</expan> et
anologia<expan type="">m</expan> ffines v<expan type="">er</expan>baliu<expan type="">m</expan> su<expan type="">n</expan>t hij
Tor Trix. Cio. T<expan type="">us</expan> Sus Me<expan type="">n</expan>s
Bundus et vra vnde versus. //.
A v<expan type="">er</expan>bis nata v<expan type="">er</expan>balia dicere cura.
ffines participior<expan type="">um</expan> sunt hij &#182; Ens
Ans Tus Sus Rus Dus et h<expan type="">ab</expan>ent
inteligi vbicu<expan type="">m</expan>q<expan type="">ue</expan> Anologia voca&#173;
bula composita non inveniuntur
In suis locis simpliciu<expan type="">m</expan> requirenda
sunt. et sic no<expan type="">m</expan>i<expan type="">n</expan>a co<expan type="">m</expan>p<expan type="">ar</expan>ac<expan type="">i</expan>o<expan type="">n</expan>es <expan type="">et</expan> adu<expan type="">er</expan>bia
ffructuu<expan type="">m</expan> g<expan type="">r</expan>amatice pu<expan type="">er</expan>is do s<expan type="">u</expan>b b<expan type="">re</expan>uita<expan type="">t</expan>e
Incipit liber intitulatus Medulla
Gramatice
